WEBVTT

00:00.360 --> 00:01.000
Your son thinks

00:01.360 --> 00:02.200
Honest advice is hard to hear

00:02.600 --> 00:03.240
But benefits action

00:03.840 --> 00:04.720
Our dynasty moved south

00:05.120 --> 00:06.360
Decades ago

00:06.840 --> 00:07.760
Yet those in the north

00:07.880 --> 00:09.440
Suffering under the Wunu

00:09.600 --> 00:10.760
Never cease longing for their homeland

00:11.360 --> 00:12.600
In these ten-plus years

00:12.760 --> 00:13.640
Our dynasty has not campaigned north

00:14.000 --> 00:15.240
Though intending to restore strength

00:16.000 --> 00:17.240
We have ignored northern hearts

00:17.480 --> 00:18.880
Abandoning the homeland and its people

00:19.480 --> 00:20.440
Is also the truth

00:21.240 --> 00:22.240
Are you saying

00:22.720 --> 00:24.120
I was wrong?

00:24.360 --> 00:25.080
Your son dares not

00:25.600 --> 00:26.360
Only wishes Father

00:26.720 --> 00:27.640
To put the realm first
